'''Carel Struycken''' portrayed [[King/Legends|King]] [[Terak]] in ''[[Ewoks: The Battle for Endor]]''. Some of Struycken's other work includes [[Wikipedia:Men in Black (film)|''Men in Black'']], the [[Wikipedia:The Addams Family|Addams Family]] films, and [[Wikipedia:The Witches of Eastwick (film)|''The Witches of Eastwick'']], and [[MemoryAlpha:Star Trek: The Next Generation|''Star Trek: The Next Generation'']] where he portrayed [[MemoryAlpha:Homn|Mr. Homn]].

